replies.body:
> None of them have damage like Yasuo.

Well, yeah. They all have much higher. It'd be much more accurate to say none of them have the mobility of Yas because Yas doesn't have their damage. 

Yi has higher mobility, damage, and survivability.
Fiora has lower mobility but higher damage and equal survivability.
Tryndamere has slightly lower mobility but much higher damage and survivability. 
Jax has low mobility but higher damage and survivability.


Out of all melee carries infact, Yasuo is one of, if not the weakest. Well, I'll give a little wiggle room for Fiora, but she's still new. He has high mobility because his damage is one of the lowest, and his survivability is nothing special. 

And if its counters you're looking for, heres a few in midlane alone.
